- Kwicara ntacyo afashe;
- Gukambakamaba akoresheje amaboko n’amavi akanagerageza guhaguruka;
- Gutera intambwe afashe ikintu;
- Kugerageza kwigana amagambo, urusaku n’ibyo abandi bakoze,
  akanasubiza bimwe mu byo asabwe;
- Gushimishwa no gukina no gukoma amashyi;
- Guterura ibintu akoresheje igikumwe n’urundi rutoki;
- Gutangira gufata ibintu nk’ikiyiko cyangwa igikombe akanager- ageza
  kwigaburira.
